                        <interp inst="t18760501-name-107" type="given" value="MARTHA"></interp>MARTHA LYON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>). This is the bad shilling I defaced with the rasp.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18760501-name-108" type="witnessName">
