                  </hi>, <hi rend="italic">a warder of Cold Bath Fields, stated that Leeson had been four times convicted, first as a rogue and vagabond, then for stealing a coat, again for being drunk, and lastly for an assault. <rs id="t18760501-351-punishment-14" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18760501-351-punishment-14" type="punishmentCategory" value="noPunish"></interp>
